    "body" : "<p>I don't know for sure for version 2, but Selenium 1 supports regular expressions in the matching. These can be marked as case-insensitive. If applicable, the following could work:</p>\n\n<pre><code>driver.findElements(By.linkText(\"regexpi:Linktext\"));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>The trailing <code>i</code> indicates a case insensitive match.</p>\n"
