    "last_activity_date" : 1665582108,
    "creation_date" : 1665582108,
    "answer_id" : 74042896,
    "question_id" : 8385459,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>An alternative would be the following:</p>\n<pre><code>// get all the a elements from the page via tagname\n    List&lt;WebElement&gt; elementList = driver.findElements(By.tagName(&quot;a&quot;));\n\n    // iterate through the list and click on element where text equals to text\n    for( WebElement ele : elementList){\n\n        if(ele.getText().equals(&quot;LINKTEXT&quot;) || ele.getText().equals(&quot;Linktext&quot;)){\n            ele.click();\n        }\n\n    }\n</code></pre>\n<p>or the following for loop:</p>\n<pre><code>for( WebElement ele : elementList){\n\n        if(ele.getText().toLowerCase().equals(&quot;linktext&quot;)){\n            ele.click();\n        }\n\n    }\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
